            "title": "黑期低水約130點 重磅港股ADR個別發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時20分跌110點或0.44%，報24644點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報24751點，較香港上日現貨收市低22點或0.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣550元，較上日香港收市高0.05元或0.01%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣118.4元，較上日香港收市高2.67元或2.31%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣120.5元，較上日香港收市低1.1元或0.91%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣123.6元，較上日香港收市高0.7元或0.57%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣52.9元，較上日香港收市低0.27元或0.51%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣96.2元，較上日香港收市高0.09元或0.09%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣73.1元，較上日香港收市低0.34元或0.46%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣424.5元，較上日香港收市低2.47元或0.58%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣54元，較上日香港收高市高0.02元或0.04%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣8元，較上日香港收市低0.05元或0.58%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報24708點，跌38點，較上日恒指收市24773點，低水65點。科指期貨夜市收報5455點，較上日科指收市高水2點；國指期貨夜市收報8872點，較上日國指收市低水11點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15138971-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%84130%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%80%8b%e5%88%a5%e7%99%bc%e5%b1%95",
